reviewText: Okay, somebody please tell me why this is sooooooooooo expensive???????? That is an insane amount of money to pay for a DVD of someone doing stand up comedy, sure it's funny, I've seen it on Comedy Central, but he wouldn't charge that much to see him live!!!!!  WHAT'S UP?????
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: Kevin James: I love him.  This is a DVD to watch with your parents & not feel embarrassed.  He puts out true life comedy that everyone can relate to in a way that is belly laugh funny while keeping it clean for all ages.

reviewText: Kevin James is a wonderful comic in the vein of Bill Cosby or Sinbad. Artists who can set up a scene, make you laugh till you're blue in the face, and never utter a curse. My only complaint is that he doesn't have more stand up films. The dvd arrived before the scheduled time, and the quality was terrific!
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: Kevin James is so funny....I loved The King of Queens....his stand up comedy is just as funny if not more at times....This DVD is great for the comedy collection....
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: This is the best stand up routine I have ever viewed. I was fortunate to have had a copy but I sent it to the troops in Iraq, they surley need a good laugh.This is a rare treat and it is kid friendly as well, something you can't say about so many other stand up routines.I recommend it to anyone, it is the BEST. Thanks Kevin James
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: Anyone can watch Kevin James. I notice that he uses no cuss words in his comedy and is still hilarious. I also appreciate the humor on weight. I watch this dvd at least once a month.
summary: Good clean fun but still funny
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: You can definitely see that Kevin James is the star in a hit sitcom because the things he acts out he acts out well. If you know King of Queens this show won't really come as a surprise: many of the situations could be episodes.The bits are not highly original. He is definitely not the first to make jokes about standing in line in the bank or at the airport. Some jokes are almost exactly the same as George Carlin once made for example.The biggest difference between someone like Carlin and James is that James is very clean. No swear words at all.Of course many of the bits are about food. The part about eating a big mac is hilarious, especially how he acts it out.It's worth seeing, especially if you like Doug Heffernan.
summary: Funny, not very original, but he is an actor
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: Kevin James is truly funny. This is a very good stand-up act. My favorite part is what I like to call "Ode to a woman picking a greeting card". Barely any words are spoken, and it was all hilarious. The act does fall flat at times, the water-skiing part was not the best. But, the cheap underwear, greeting cards and little things to bring up after a date: they were all hilarious.
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: Kevin James is so funny in this video! He puts the awkward moments in life that everyone has been through and makes you laugh about them! :) I loved this DVD and watch it over and over when I need a laugh, or if I don't! Good job Kevin James! It's a little over-priced, only because there aren't many available but I think it's worth if you like Kevin James.
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: This show is so hard to get in DVD format ... in ANY format so if you can find it, grab it!  Kevin James is hilarious and has a clean show.
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff

reviewText: First of all let me say I am a huge Kevin James and King of Queens fan so I may be biased. However, I have seen tons of "Comedy Central Presents" routines and many hour comedy specials buy guys like Jeff Dunham, Christopher Titus, Dane Cook, etc and this is the funniest routine I have EVER seen. I have watched it at least 10 times and I still can laugh at it despite knowing every joke.Kevin can make you laugh without using a sear word every other word. How does he do it? By telling jokes and stories about every day life. It makes it that much funnier when you can relate to jokes.Bottom line: it may be expensive but it is well worth it. This is something you will enjoy over and over again.
summary: FUNNIEST STANDUP ROUTINE I HAVE EVER SEEN!
Title: Kevin James - Sweat the Small Stuff
